s such as:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>PVP free for all pooping<br></li><li>Team vs Team pooping<br></li><li>Zombie horde co-op<br></li><li>Play as a parent vs pooplers<br></li><li>Play silly football match as a toddler! </li></ul><br>Play with Friends or learn new tactics alone, with bots. Poop in!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177170/extras/b73d05161607c439158592c0c1372939.avif?t=1671724427\" width=610 height=610 /></span>",
